  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics Based Golfing</h2>Switch between the driver, wood, iron, and putter, each offering a different way to tackle the courses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/5c4cfbf652c5d1671e610067f956613e.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/5c4cfbf652c5d1671e610067f956613e.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/5c4cfbf652c5d1671e610067f956613e.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Platforming</h2>Golfing is just the beginning. Leap, dash, and navigate through tricky platforming segments.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/55849b483ea4c1d3da8dbc6dbbca28b9.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/55849b483ea4c1d3da8dbc6dbbca28b9.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/55849b483ea4c1d3da8dbc6dbbca28b9.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2>Play online with up to 12 friends. Or if you're feeling adventurous, join public lobbies and meet new golfing buddies!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/623f609f14e4cba2043d54f94888f949.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/623f609f14e4cba2043d54f94888f949.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/623f609f14e4cba2043d54f94888f949.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2>Unleash your creativity with the built-in level editor. Design custom levels and share them with the community through the Steam Workshop. Play and rate community-created maps for endless golfing adventures!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/a90ce407f8b27da1a4a00822666f90f8.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/a90ce407f8b27da1a4a00822666f90f8.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/a90ce407f8b27da1a4a00822666f90f8.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Give Us Feedback!</h2>",
